@token = paste_session_token_here
@otherToken = paste_other_session_token_here
@roomId = paste_room_id_here

### Login — creates new user and returns session token
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"username": "ali_123"}

###

### Login again — same user.id, fresh session token
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"username": "ali_123"}

###

### Validation error — username too short (min 2)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"username": "a"}

###

### Validation error — invalid characters (space not allowed)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"username": "ali 123"}

###

### Validation error — username too long (max 24)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"username": "this_username_is_way_too_long_123"}

###

### Auth guard — missing token should return 401
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/rooms

###

### ── ROOMS ────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create room (requires valid token)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "general"}

###

### Create room — duplicate name → 409 ROOM_NAME_TAKEN
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "general"}

###

### Create room — invalid chars → 400 VALIDATION_ERROR
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "bad name!"}

###

### List all rooms
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get room by id
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/rooms/{{roomId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get room — not found → 404 ROOM_NOT_FOUND
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/rooms/room_000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Delete room (must be creator)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/rooms/{{roomId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Delete room by non-creator → 403 FORBIDDEN
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/rooms/{{roomId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{otherToken}}
